  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Open Challenges under Gamification.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 1.351,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "This is the Challenge Board.",
      "startS": 1.351,
      "endS": 3.679,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "WashCentral turns your everyday targets into a running competition here,",
      "startS": 3.679,
      "endS": 7.363,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "with points on the line and a deadline on every one.",
      "startS": 7.363,
      "endS": 11.079,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "It's what keeps a crew pushing when the lobby goes quiet.",
      "startS": 11.079,
      "endS": 15.009,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "Start at the top.",
      "startS": 15.44,
      "endS": 16.562,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "Five numbers sum up the whole program at a glance:",
      "startS": 17.524,
      "endS": 20.512,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "how many challenges exist, how many are live, how many finished,",
      "startS": 20.822,
      "endS": 24.582,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "how many are about to start, and how many slipped past their deadline.",
      "startS": 24.902,
      "endS": 28.539,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "One row, and you know where the program stands.",
      "startS": 28.95,
      "endS": 31.6,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Glance down the Gamification group.",
      "startS": 32.053,
      "endS": 33.973,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "Six pages sit together: the board you're on,",
      "startS": 34.452,
      "endS": 35.861,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "plus the leaderboard, targets, prizes, a recognition feed, and pulse surveys.",
      "startS": 36.333,
      "endS": 42.599,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "Today we stay on Challenges.",
      "startS": 43.302,
      "endS": 44.989,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "Just know the rest of the program lives one click away.",
      "startS": 45.553,
      "endS": 48.379,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "Now the board itself, Active and Upcoming Challenges.",
      "startS": 48.8,
      "endS": 49.924,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Three controls sit up top: Active, All, and Completed.",
      "startS": 50.408,
      "endS": 52.434,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "They only change what you're looking at, never the data underneath.",
      "startS": 53.512,
      "endS": 54.955,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "And that green New Challenge button?",
      "startS": 55.287,
      "endS": 55.797,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "Leave it alone today.",
      "startS": 56.112,
      "endS": 57.375,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Building challenges is a manager's job.",
      "startS": 57.815,
      "endS": 67.654,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Take the first live card.",
      "startS": 68.168,
      "endS": 69.707,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "A ring shows how far along the team is.",
      "startS": 70.075,
      "endS": 78.092,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "Beside it, the reward in points, who it's for, when it ends, and how many days are left.",
      "startS": 78.417,
      "endS": 79.703,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Then the hard number: washes done against the goal.",
      "startS": 80.082,
      "endS": 81.954,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "That's the whole story of the challenge in one glance.",
      "startS": 82.317,
      "endS": 85.193,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "Look lower on the same card.",
      "startS": 85.6,
      "endS": 87.575,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "A cluster of avatars and a headcount tell you who's taking part.",
      "startS": 88.248,
      "endS": 92.41,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Off to the right, the current leader and their score.",
      "startS": 93.089,
      "endS": 95.825,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "So a technician can answer two questions fast:",
      "startS": 96.207,
      "endS": 98.795,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "how's the team doing, and who's out front.",
      "startS": 99.132,
      "endS": 101.36,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "The other two live cards read exactly the same way.",
      "startS": 101.76,
      "endS": 104.683,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "One tracks upsell dollars, another tracks attendance.",
      "startS": 105.296,
      "endS": 108.57,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Only the metric and its unit change from card to card.",
      "startS": 109.283,
      "endS": 112.366,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "Learn one card and you've learned them all.",
      "startS": 112.887,
      "endS": 114.96,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Below the live ones, the challenges warming up.",
      "startS": 115.445,
      "endS": 117.945,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Same shape, but instead of progress you get a start date and the rule for winning.",
      "startS": 118.593,
      "endS": 123.111,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Each one carries an Edit button.",
      "startS": 124.098,
      "endS": 125.799,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "That's a manager's control, so we read it and move on.",
      "startS": 126.11,
      "endS": 129.334,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "At the end of that row, a dashed tile invites you to create a new challenge.",
      "startS": 129.822,
      "endS": 134.131,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "It's the second door into the same builder.",
      "startS": 134.427,
      "endS": 136.611,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "We're reviewing, not building, so we leave it closed.",
      "startS": 136.872,
      "endS": 139.799,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "Now try the All view.",
      "startS": 140.24,
      "endS": 141.671,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "The board widens to every challenge, while the numbers up top hold steady.",
      "startS": 142.018,
      "endS": 146.052,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Notice what didn't happen: nothing was edited or sent.",
      "startS": 146.988,
      "endS": 148.489,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "You're just changing the lens.",
      "startS": 148.813,
      "endS": 152.32,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "Switch to Completed.",
      "startS": 152.72,
      "endS": 153.888,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "Here are the challenges that already wrapped,",
      "startS": 154.455,
      "endS": 156.57,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "and the count lines up with the Completed figure you read at the top.",
      "startS": 156.888,
      "endS": 160.168,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "This is where you'd look back to see how a past competition landed.",
      "startS": 160.776,
      "endS": 164.061,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "Click back to Active.",
      "startS": 164.48,
      "endS": 165.86,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "The live and upcoming cards return, right where they were.",
      "startS": 166.309,
      "endS": 169.425,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "Three views, one board, and switching between them never touches a thing.",
      "startS": 169.747,
      "endS": 173.76,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "So that's Gamification.",
      "startS": 174.217,
      "endS": 175.232,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "The KPIs count the whole program,",
      "startS": 175.232,
      "endS": 177.661,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "the Active view shows what's live and what's coming,",
      "startS": 177.661,
      "endS": 180.934,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "and every card reads the same once you know the pattern.",
      "startS": 180.934,
      "endS": 185.15,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p58",
      "text": "When you need the wider picture,",
      "startS": 185.15,
      "endS": 187.181,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p59",
      "text": "the leaderboard, targets, prizes, recognition, and surveys are right there in the sidebar.",
      "startS": 187.181,
      "endS": 191.58,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p60",
      "text": "Read the board, point people to it, and leave the building to the managers.",
      "startS": 191.58,
      "endS": 196.64,
      "timing": "proportional"
    }
  ]
}